cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a query-based generative model for question generation and question answering, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also leverages reinforcement learning algorithms, which falls under the scope of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The model uses attention-based LSTM, which is a popular deep learning technique in cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves information retrieval techniques, which is related to cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the model uses neural networks, which is a common technique in cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
